snippet: The chip maker has agreed to acquire Telmap, a mobile software company based in Israel, Telmap’s chief executive said. The terms of the deal weren’t disclosed.
lead_paragraph: The chip maker has agreed to acquire Telmap, a mobile software company based in Israel, Telmap’s chief executive said. The terms of the deal weren’t disclosed.
